markdownRemark.html:
• Hey Amigas! I am Sanjana Maheshwari. A Computer Engineering Sophomore at Zakir Husain College of Engineering and technology.
  • I aspire to become an excellent Software Engineer. I like to try new stuff and see what comes out of them. For instance - This blog site is my second attempt. I chose some wrong tech stack and super colorful CSS xD. I messed it. It was a great lesson for me.
  • I write a lot of code and love learning new algorithms. It gives me the confidence to tackle problems quickly and think efficiently.
  • I recently became quite interested in cryptography and making some super beginner projects in same. I will try to write about them here.
  • My hobbies include knowing about different cultures and people. I am working with a non-profit organization that aims at imparting education to underprivileged children(This is a story for another blog!).
  • That’s a wrap! The list will elongate in the coming years. Bear with me xD.
  • Thank you!
